OL,3,CFamily's renewed calls for assisted
OL,4,Cdying ahead of parliamentary debate
OL,6,FRachel Bullock has been speaking to
OL,7,Fthe family of Ray Craven who travelled
OL,8,Fto Switzerland to end his life
OL,10,FA Tyneside family has renewed its
OL,11,Fcalls for the UK government to allow
OL,12,Fassisted dying ahead of a bill being
OL,13,Fheard in Parliament.
OL,15,FNaomi Craven travelled to Switzerland
OL,16,Fwith her father Ray Craven, from North
OL,17,FShields, to end his life aged 70,
OL,18,Ffollowing his battle with Motor
OL,19,FNeurone Disease.
