OL,3,CFamily's renewed calls for assisted
OL,4,Cdying ahead of parliamentary debate
OL,6,F"He was robbed of having time with his
OL,7,Ffamily, time with his friends, and I
OL,8,Fjust don't think that's right.
OL,10,F"The journey to Switzerland was
OL,11,Fabsolutely awful.
OL,13,F"You're travelling with somebody who
OL,14,Fis very, very ill and is leaving their
OL,15,Fhome for the last time.
OL,17,F"My dad was very much a Geordie, he
OL,18,Falways wanted to to live out his days
OL,19,Fin Newcastle."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/8
