OL,3,CFamily's renewed calls for assisted
OL,4,Cdying ahead of parliamentary debate
OL,6,FAsked whether or not breaking the law
OL,7,Fto help her father had phased her
OL,8,FNaomi replied: "Absolutely, it's
OL,9,Fobviously something that you worry
OL,10,Fabout.
OL,12,F"But when it's your family member in
OL,13,Fthat sort of position, I think that
OL,14,Fyou would do whatever you needed to do
OL,15,Fis support them."
