OL,3,CFamily's renewed calls for assisted
OL,4,Cdying ahead of parliamentary debate
OL,6,FShe said: "I know people say it's all
OL,7,Fgiven the choice and that's really
OL,8,Fimportant but there are also going to
OL,9,Fbe a lot of people who feel that they
OL,10,Fhave no choice but to end their lives.
OL,12,F"We know that doctors and even the
OL,13,Fpolice are not good at spotting
OL,14,Fcoercive control."
OL,16,FThe Stockton-based peer worries that
OL,17,Frelatives could coerce vulnerable
OL,18,Findividuals into assisted dying,
OL,19,Fadding: "Where there's a will there's
OL,20,Fa relative."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/8
