OL,3,CFamily's renewed calls for assisted
OL,4,Cdying ahead of parliamentary debate
OL,6,FDr Jonathan Romain, who supports the
OL,7,Fbill, said: "The bill is going to be
OL,8,Freally safe in terms of ensuring that
OL,9,Feverything is done properly.
OL,11,F"Frankly, I wouldn't support it
OL,12,Fotherwise, but still, they have to be
OL,13,Fterminally ill, they have to be
OL,14,Fmentally competent and it also has to
OL,15,Fbe of their own free will.
OL,17,F"One of the ways that is ensured is by
OL,18,Fbeing interviewed by two doctors
OL,19,Fseparately.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/8
