OL,6,F"If you are dying in agony and you
OL,7,Fwant to let go, then I think people
OL,8,Fshould have that option."
OL,10,FThe bill will be introduced in
OL,11,FParliament on 16 October, and MPs will
OL,12,Fvote on it in the coming months.
